Educational License – CentroWeg – Systems Development Course
Class MIDS 77

Copyright (c) 2024 Carlos Eduardo Braga

This software was developed exclusively for educational purposes as part of the Systems Development course at CentroWeg, Class MIDS 77, during the Database curricular unit, under the guidance of professor Kristian Erdmann and with contributions and assistance from other teachers.

Granted permissions:
- Anyone may view, copy, or fork this code for personal or educational purposes.
- It is allowed to study, learn from, and use it as a reference for personal database development.
- Running the SQL scripts as provided in this repository is permitted.
- It is allowed to use the database structures as a basis for educational projects.

Restrictions:
- Direct modification of this code and redistribution as the original is not allowed.
- Changes may only be made in personal copies or forks, provided the reference to the original code and author is preserved.
- Commercial use is prohibited without the express permission of the author.
- It is not allowed to use sensitive or personal data in examples or exercises.
- It is mandatory to use only fictitious data for educational purposes.

Disclaimer:
The software is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.
In no event shall the author, teachers, or the institution be liable for any claim, damages, or other liability arising from, out of, or in connection with the software or its use.
The author is not responsible for data loss or security issues arising from the use of the provided SQL scripts.